Lumos offers clean and affordable solar power to a market of 1.3 billion potential customers who live off the electricity grid.Lumos enables people to replace hazardous and expensive kerosene generators and lanterns with modern solar electricity that can power lights, cellphones, fans, computers, TVs and other small electronic devices (all at once, every day). By offering Solar Power as a Service, Lumos offers homes and small businesses a simple and affordable way to pay for electricity in small installments using their mobile phones We are recruiting to fill the position below:

Job Title: Territory Sales Officer Location: Osun/Ekiti
Reporting Relationship (Line Manager): Regional Manager
Function: Sales Purpose Job Responsibilities Requirements
Educational Qualifications & Functional / Technical Skills: Relevant Experience: Other Requirements: Application Closing Date
